OL,3,CPeople put off city because of 'crime
OL,4,Cand poor transport'
OL,6,FPlans worth #20m to revive the
OL,7,Ffortunes of Wrexham city centre have
OL,8,Fbeen outlined following claims that
OL,9,Fcrime and poor transport links are
OL,10,Fcausing residents to spend huge sums
OL,11,Felsewhere.
OL,13,FIn September 2023, Wrexham was
OL,14,Fannounced as one of 55 towns and
OL,15,Fcities selected to take part in the UK
OL,16,FGovernment's Long-Term Plan for Towns
OL,17,Fscheme.
OL,19,FIt means the city could receive up to
OL,20,F#20m over the next ten years to help
OL,21,Fdeliver improvements.
