OL,3,CPeople put off city because of 'crime
OL,4,Cand poor transport'
OL,6,FA report has now been revealed by
OL,7,Fmembers of the Wrexham City Board,
OL,8,Fwhich includes community and business
OL,9,Fleaders, detailing how they intend to
OL,10,Fboost the area's economy.
OL,12,FThe ten-year plan will serve as a
OL,13,Fbusiness case to secure government
OL,14,Finvestment, with the initial tranche
OL,15,Fto be spent over the next three years.
OL,17,FIt shows how a range of issues are
OL,18,Fcausing people living in Wrexham to
OL,19,Fspend tens of millions of pounds in
OL,20,Fnearby towns and shopping centres
OL,21,Finstead of their own city.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/10
