OL,6,FThe document states: "The city centre
OL,7,Ffaces numerous challenges. Some relate
OL,8,Fto the prevailing general decline
OL,9,Fexperienced by most town and city
OL,10,Fcentres throughout the UK, and others
OL,11,Fare specific to Wrexham.
OL,13,F"Although #101m is spent annually by
OL,14,Fresidents in Wrexham city centre, with
OL,15,Fan additional #6m spent by workers and
OL,16,F#6m by tourists (totalling #113m)
OL,17,Fthere is significant leakage of spend
OL,18,Ffrom the local population.
