OL,3,CPeople put off city because of 'crime
OL,4,Cand poor transport'
OL,6,F"Those living in Wrexham spend more
OL,7,F(#137m) in Cheshire Oaks, Broughton
OL,8,Fand Oswestry, which are all out of
OL,9,Fcounty. They also spend #72m online."
OL,11,FIt adds: "Out of town shopping and
OL,12,Fleisure destinations are also having
OL,13,Fan impact, #41m is spent in Plas Coch,
OL,14,Fwhich acts to intercept visitors
OL,15,Fbefore they reach the centre of the
OL,16,Fcity.
OL,18,F"Wrexham's numerous out of town retail
OL,19,Fparks are favoured due to their
OL,20,Fconvenience and are often the default
OL,21,Fchoice of many time-poor households."
