OL,6,FThe report highlights high crime rates
OL,7,Fas one of the main problems needing to
OL,8,Fbe addressed.
OL,10,FIt follows figures being released
OL,11,Fwhich show the city's crime rate is
OL,12,Fnearly double the Welsh average at 181
OL,13,Fincidents per 1,000 of the population.
OL,15,FThe report states: "Available data and
OL,16,Fengagement activity undertaken by the
OL,17,FWrexham City Board indicates that
OL,18,Fsafety is recognised as an issue of
OL,19,Fgreater concern in Wrexham than many
OL,20,Fother parts of Wales.
OL,26,@wD@TOU
