OL,3,CPeople put off city because of 'crime
OL,4,Cand poor transport'
OL,6,F"In 2023, the recorded crime rate was
OL,7,Fhigher than the Wales average both
OL,8,Facross Wrexham county borough and more
OL,9,Fsignificantly in the city centre area.
OL,11,F"Data commissioned by the Wrexham City
OL,12,FBoard from North Wales Police
OL,13,Findicates that crime has declined in
OL,14,Fall categories across Wrexham's city
OL,15,Fcentre 'beat area' over the past three
OL,16,Fyears.
OL,18,F"Despite this improvement, the city
OL,19,Fcentre remains a hotspot for both
OL,20,Fcrime and anti-social behaviour."
