OL,3,CPeople put off city because of 'crime
OL,4,Cand poor transport'
OL,6,FThe most frequent crimes reported in
OL,7,F2023 were violence without injury
OL,8,F(2,101 incidents), theft and handling
OL,9,F(1,675), and anti-social behaviour
OL,10,F(1,443).
OL,12,FWithin the city centre, the bus
OL,13,Fstation and Crescent Road area were
OL,14,Fflagged as the main hotspots for anti-
OL,15,Fsocial behaviour.
OL,17,FCrime in general was most prevalent on
OL,18,Fa section of the High Street nearest
OL,19,FTown Hill and Abbot Street, where many
OL,20,Fof the city's nightspots are located.
