OL,6,FMeasures proposed to address the
OL,7,Fissues include introducing city centre
OL,8,Fwardens, improving CCTV systems and
OL,9,Finstalling automatic rising bollards
OL,10,Fto manage key locations.
OL,12,FTransport and parking issues in
OL,13,FWrexham are also reported to have made
OL,14,Fresidents spend elsewhere.
OL,16,FThe report states: "Wrexham, part of
OL,17,Fthe North Wales transport region,
OL,18,Falong with Flintshire, has a high
OL,19,Fdependency on car travel, with 84 per
OL,20,Fcent of journeys made by car.
