OL,6,F"Despite the area having the highest
OL,7,Fproportion of the population with
OL,8,Faccess to hourly public transport
OL,9,Fduring peak morning hours (73 per
OL,10,Fcent), this figure drops significantly
OL,11,Fduring evenings, weekends, and Sundays.
OL,13,F"To enhance Wrexham's transport
OL,14,Fnetwork, there is a need to improve
OL,15,Fthe frequency and hours of public
OL,16,Ftransport services and make driving
OL,17,Fless appealing to promote
OL,18,Fsustainability."
