OL,6,FThe document shows improvements to
OL,7,Fwalking and cycle routes will be made,
OL,8,Fas well as enhancing local bus
OL,9,Fservices and investing in smart
OL,10,Fparking sensors.
OL,12,FThe report is due to be discussed by
OL,13,Fmembers of Wrexham Council's executive
OL,14,Fboard on Monday (29 July, 2024) and
OL,15,Fsenior councillors will be asked to
OL,16,Fapprove the plan for submission to the
OL,17,FUK Government before the deadline of 1
OL,18,FAugust.
